{
  "llm": "gemini",
  "channel_history_limit": 0,
  "graph": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "gemini_main",
        "type": "GEMINI_CLI",
        "model": "gemini-2.5-pro",
        "session_key": "jei_main",
        "enable_routing": true,
        "permission_mode": "plan",
        "timeout": 120,
        "system_prompt": "你是知识策展官，负责管理和展现知识资产。\n\n## 可用执行助手\n\n1. **knowledge_shelf**：搜索、读取、创建、修改 Obsidian Vault 中的笔记。\n   路由信号：{\"route\": \"knowledge_shelf\", \"context\": \"具体任务描述\"}\n\n## 路由规则\n\n- 需要操作 Vault 笔记时，输出路由信号（JSON 独占第一行，之后不要写任何内容）\n- 无需路由时直接回复用户，不要输出 JSON\n- 收到 [子图结论] 后，基于结论整理回复给用户\n- 若需多步操作（如先搜索再修改），每次只路由一步，等结论回来再决定下一步\n\n## 路由信号格式（严格遵守）\n\n第一行且仅第一行输出 JSON，不加任何前缀：\n{\"route\": \"knowledge_shelf\", \"context\": \"你的具体指令\"}\n\n## 示例\n\n用户：帮我搜一下关于分布式系统的笔记\n你的输出（仅此一行）：\n{\"route\": \"knowledge_shelf\", \"context\": \"搜索 Vault 中与'分布式系统'相关的笔记，返回文件路径和摘要\"}"
      },
      {
        "id": "validate",
        "type": "VALIDATE"
      },
      {
        "id": "knowledge_shelf",
        "type": "SUBGRAPH_REF",
        "agent_dir": "blueprints/functional_graphs/knowledge_shelf",
        "max_retry": 2,
        "state_in": {
          "task": "routing_context",
          "knowledge_vault": "knowledge_vault"
        },
        "state_out": {
          "knowledge_result": "last_message"
        }
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "id": "e_start_2_gemini",
        "from": "__start__",
        "to": "gemini_main"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_gemini_2_validate",
        "from": "gemini_main",
        "to": "validate"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_validate_2_shelf",
        "type": "routing_to",
        "from": "validate",
        "to": "knowledge_shelf"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_validate_2_end",
        "type": "no_routing",
        "from": "validate",
        "to": "__end__"
      },
      {
        "id": "e_shelf_2_gemini",
        "from": "knowledge_shelf",
        "to": "gemini_main"
      }
    ]
  },
  "max_retries": 2,
  "persona_files": [
    "ROLE.md",
    "PROTOCOL.md"
  ]
}
